'''Amor Hakkar''' (  yavutse ku ya 1 Mutarama 1958), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Aligeriya|Alijeriya]] akaba na producer<ref>Amor Hakkar - Fiche Personne sur Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › personnes</ref>, umwanditsi wa sinema ndetse n'umukinnyi ukora ubu mu bucuruzi bwa firime mu [[Bufaransa]].  Afite isosiyete ikora firime "Sarah Films"<ref>Amor Hakkar | IFFR <nowiki>https://iffr.com</nowiki> › people › amor-hakkar</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 1 Mutarama 1958 mu mudugudu w’imisozi Aurès mu karere ka Khenchela muri [[Aligeriya|Alijeriya]]. Afite amezi 6, yageze mu [[Bufaransa]] ari kumwe n'ababyeyi be.  Kuva icyo gihe, babaga i Besançon, mucyaro, umujyi wa Founottes.  Se Chays Hakkar yamugizeho ingaruka zo kwiga siyanse<ref>Amor Hakkar - AlloCiné <nowiki>https://www.allocine.fr</nowiki> › person</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1990, Hakkar yayoboye filime ye ya mbere ngufi yise''Teach me to count to infinity'' . Noneho mu 1992, yakoze film yambere yise ''Bad Time for a Thug'' . Wari umurimo ukorana na Pierre-Loup Rajot, Sylvie Fennec na Serge Giamberardino kandi wakozwe na sosiyete Rage au cœur film<ref>Amor Hakkar : Récompenses et nominations - AlloCiné (allocine.fr)</ref>. 

Mu 1994, yatangiye gufata amashusho mu [[Bufaransa]] no mu [[Butaliyani]] filime ''Ailleurs c'est beau aussi'' hamwe na Mado Maurin na Pierre Remund<ref>Amor Hakkar - UniFrance <nowiki>https://en.unifrance.org</nowiki> › directories › person › amor-h...</ref>. Hanyuma mu 1998, Hakkar yimukiye mu karere kavukire ka Aurès gushyingura ibisigazwa bya se, aho yafashe amashusho ya firime ya televiziyo yitwa ''Timgad, la vie au cœur des Aurès'', documentaire y’iminota 52 kuri TV 5 y’Ubufaransa<ref>Amor Hakkar - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › cast › amor-hakkar</ref>.  Hagati aho, mu 2001, yatsindiye igihembo cya Marcel Aymé kubera igitabo cyitwa ''La cité des fausses notes'' .  Mu 2005, Hakkar yashinze isosiyete ikora firime Sarah Films<ref>Amor Hakkar - Premiere <nowiki>https://www.premiere.fr</nowiki> › Star › Am...</ref>. 

Muri 2015, yayoboye filime ''Celle qui vivra'' hamwe na Meryem Medjkane, Muriel Racine, Nicolas Dufour, Hichem Berdouk na Caroline Fouilhoux. Iyi filime yatewe inkunga na sinema y'umwimerere na Florence Bouteloup ndetse na filime yasohotse mu makinamico mu 2017. Muri 2018, yayoboye filime ''Le Choix d'Ali''<ref>Amor Hakkar | BFI <nowiki>https://www2.bfi.org.uk</nowiki> › movies-tv-people</ref> . 

